&lt;p&gt;Iran launched another round of missile and drone attacks targeting Bahrain and Kuwait on Sunday in response to fresh US airstrikes, warning that negotiations to end the conflict would come to a &quot;complete halt&quot; if Washington continued its military campaign.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The latest exchange marks a further escalation in hostilities despite an interim agreement aimed at reducing tensions between the two countries.&lt;/p&gt;
